---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Aarith Veerabhadran" description="A little extra">
  <section
    class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-20 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] lg:items-center lg:gap-6"
  >
    <div class="lg:pr-6">
      <p class="mb-3 font-sans text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-terracotta-dark">
        About
      </p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-ink sm:text-5xl">
        A little more about me
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-lg text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink-soft">
        Placeholder: I grew up taking things apart to see how they worked, which is either a
        good origin story for an engineer or a bad habit, depending who you ask (my parents
        would say the latter). These days that same curiosity mostly points at brains — how
        billions of noisy, imperfect cells manage to produce something as coherent as a memory
        or a decision — but it still shows up in side projects, in my photography, and in
        whatever I happen to be reading that week.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-lg text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink-soft">
        Placeholder: I'm currently [year] studying [major] at [school], splitting my time
        between a research lab, a handful of software projects, and a camera I take more
        places than is strictly reasonable. I like collaborators who ask good questions more
        than ones who already have all the answers, and I'm always up for a conversation about
        neuroscience, machine learning, or where to find good light for a photo.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative mt-16 lg:mt-0 lg:-mr-12 xl:-mr-24">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <img
          src="/images/headshot.svg"
          alt="Placeholder headshot — swap for a real photo"
          width="480"
          height="480"
          class="col-span-2 w-full max-w-[15rem] -rotate-2 rounded-2xl border-8 border-white object-cover shadow-xl sm:col-span-1 sm:max-w-none"
        />
        <img
          src="/images/aarith_tennis_photo.jpeg"
          alt="Hitting a forehand on the tennis court"
          width="561"
          height="749"
          class="mt-6 w-full max-w-[10rem] rotate-3 justify-self-end rounded-2xl border-8 border-white object-cover shadow-xl sm:mt-0 sm:max-w-none sm:self-end"
        />
        <img
          src="/images/aarith_baby_photo_thinking.jpeg"
          alt="As a baby, deep in thought"
          width="1280"
          height="960"
          class="col-span-2 -mt-4 w-full max-w-[12rem] -rotate-1 justify-self-center rounded-2xl border-8 border-white object-cover shadow-xl sm:col-span-1 sm:mt-8 sm:max-w-none sm:justify-self-start"
        />
        <img
          src="/images/aarith_mama_photo_pv.jpeg"
          alt="With my mom on a river cruise at night"
          width="1280"
          height="855"
          class="col-span-2 mt-2 w-full max-w-[15rem] rotate-2 justify-self-center rounded-2xl border-8 border-white object-cover shadow-xl sm:max-w-none sm:justify-self-end"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
